headline: Cloverdale Paint Group Launches new "Made in Canada" Rodda Paint brand at Select Costco Warehouse Locations
summary: Cloverdale Paint with their subsidiary Rodda Miller Paint, is excited to announce the introduction of a brand-new Interior Paint Program available now at select Costco test warehouse locations. This exclusive program offers Costco members access to premium-quality interior paint at an exceptional value, reinforcing Costco's commitment to convenience, quality, and customer satisfaction.

headline: TEAMSTERS FILE WAGE THEFT COMPLAINT AGAINST COSTCO
summary: Teamsters Local 174 has filed multiple official complaints with the Washington State Department of Labor and Industries after Costco Wholesale blatantly refused to pay fleet drivers the wages guaranteed under their collective bargaining agreement.
